lead_paragraph: Colombian Camilo Villegas, Canadian rookie Mackenzie Hughes, Swede Henrik Norlander and American Blayne Barber will return to complete a playoff for the PGA Tour's RSM Classic in Georgia on Monday as darkness halted play after two extra holes.

headline.print_headline: PGA Tour Event Playoff Carrying Over to Monday
